metadata.name: Suspension
metadata.description:
Her first look at life, is a look full of Confusion, Imagines, Rules, Feels and Wills.
Lost in a world that is infinitely vast and
Suspended in a endless time !
A world that is unconsciously present to her at every moment of awakening but does not surrender to her . 
Rather, it extends in a fixed hierarchy from existence to infinite transcendence.
The world that is present to her now has a temporal horizon in its infinity on both sides, in its known and unknown, in its near and past life and its lifeless future.As if her world is collapsing ! 
Finds itself at all times without being able to change it and is in relation to a world that remains as it is forever in its constant change.
In the End She was Alone ! In a way No one understands…

Music By kiarash baktashian
